{"tid":2037031,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"曼德拉點樣贏？睇完再諗點做","createTime":"2020-05-26T20:48:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T12:02:48.000Z","uid":153938,"like":129,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"6d349768898c33f4b31e7917168aabe953ad3497","tid":2037031,"uid":153938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T20:48:37.000Z","msg":"曼德拉50年代開始反抗種族隔離，一開始淨係行和理非路線。<br />\n1960年發生南非版六四<span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>「\u001d沙佩維爾屠殺」</strong></span></span>，黑警射死咗69個示威者。<br />\n之後曼德拉嘅組織（非國大）知道搞和理非路線冇用，轉咗做地下組織。<br />\n而跟住佢畀人拉咗去坐監。<br />\n去到80年代，非國大定咗四大方針，講點樣推冧隔離措施。<br />\n四大方針係：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">群眾動員</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">武裝行動</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">地下組織</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">國際連結</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你估邊個係最緊要？<br />\n非國大話係<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> <span style=\"color: orange;\">群眾動員</span></span></strong>。<br />\n非國大嘅策略好明確，係要透過公民不合作、罷工以及破壞重要設施令政府<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">「無法管治」</span></span></strong>，迫政府做真正的談判。<br />\n但如果淨係得群眾動員，你估政府會唔會即刻就<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">「無法管治」</span></span></strong>，或者真係談判？<br />\n所以發生南非六四後，非國大著手發展後面三樣，目的係：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">分化同減弱統治階級，壯大反抗勢力。</span></span></strong><br />\n即係削弱對手，加強同伴。<br />\n<br />\n可能你會問，有得武裝勢力，做乜唔直接剷冧南非政府？<br />\n至少喺非國大嚟講，武裝勢力只係破壞手段，而實際上有冇可能咁易打贏一個國家？我諗大家心知肚明。非國大講嘅係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">「\u001d四大方針」</span></strong></span>，如果得個打字，好明顯「國際連結」就唔駛做。<br />\n非國大由始至終，都係要搞到<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">政府管治唔到，被迫談判。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n但係，如果只係單搞群眾動員就有效，就唔會有「南非六四」，曼德拉唔駛坐27年監。\b非國大最後係同政府談判然後奪權，不過後面連住一堆<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">國家</span></span></strong>同<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">武器</span></span></strong>，甚至<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">商家</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n\b而家問你，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">一日內有冇可能\b迫到政府埋枱投降？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n當然，就算冇，唔代表做咩都冇用。每次行動都係累積嘅一部份。<br />\n但要累積到終有一日可以反枱，就唔可以成日當Endgame咁諗。諗下現階段可以做到啲乜，唔駛All-in。南非人決定以身捐國前，起碼係拎住支槍。<br />\n<br />\n\b簡單啲講，今日只係其中一日，做到效果固然好，冇唔代表所有嘢玩完，請量力而為。咁講好殘酷，但我哋<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">已經被揀中</span></span></strong>，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢一世注定同佢賭</span></span></strong>。既然有排賭，請唔好咁快all-in輸身家。"},{"pid":"34907eedc7585d2386565594607a91462a148908","tid":2037031,"uid":153938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T20:49:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dbf385acb918aac86c66a6cb220f634f115ef919","tid":2037031,"uid":153938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T20:52:15.000Z","msg":"大家 Be water"},{"pid":"0a27cbe8ecf5430768bbb39e15915f2fb82d9d53","tid":2037031,"uid":74334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T21:01:23.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"fbb4645623d13e1e4c0f20f6e9ab1ff473d0121e","tid":2037031,"uid":153938,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T21:04:37.000Z","msg":"南非人仲有搞「黑人經濟圈」，同樣係針對政府弱點去做。<br />\n我哋仲有好多嘢未做，唔好覺得呢刻就完。"},{"pid":"9e0f704e148b5ba76729ea4eeb34339c87bfbb9b","tid":2037031,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T21:06:04.000Z","msg":"香港咁細好難搞地下組織"},{"pid":"3fec694059b2172793daf4cb7add75bd3426ec80","tid":2037031,"uid":318780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T21:06:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c542823171daaf36fc6fe639ceea003364853f84","tid":2037031,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T21:08:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7e11acbc0b3a4b15dceb889508b963f69cf36893","tid":2037031,"uid":153938,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T21:10:42.000Z","msg":"地下組織難搞，都唔夠喺呢刻衝散三萬警犬難吧。<br />\n我重點係，人哋有好多方面去做，如果呢刻見到死路，唔好即刻絕望送死。"},{"pid":"d67d7b6bfe279252cc2caedfdb68eba0c7070e25","tid":2037031,"uid":71262,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T21:15:55.000Z","msg":"今晚終於見到正常既連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔洗絕望 唔係end game <br />\n仲有成世 身心都要鬥長命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n絕不認命！"},{"pid":"96a12b18f22d8be00d0faca356e134f72d5ea3e3","tid":2037031,"uid":41423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T21:32:31.000Z","msg":"四大戰線同時進行"},{"pid":"3bc37512732b3d95e74c285e2bd30ffa7b487edd","tid":2037031,"uid":153938,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"d67d7b6bfe279252cc2caedfdb68eba0c7070e25","tid":2037031,"uid":71262,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T21:15:55.000Z","msg":"今晚終於見到正常既連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔洗絕望 唔係end game <br />\n仲有成世 身心都要鬥長命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n絕不認命！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T21:32:59.000Z","msg":"梁繼平話，真正連結香港人的，是痛苦。<br />\n抗爭係會痛苦，但我哋會一齊撐落去。"},{"pid":"2e6150942715a24e1be90926d68db69bc6389bb3","tid":2037031,"uid":332877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T21:33:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6de29ffa46ecba56fa75dab329374b4b4685801","tid":2037031,"uid":153938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"96a12b18f22d8be00d0faca356e134f72d5ea3e3","tid":2037031,"uid":41423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T21:32:31.000Z","msg":"四大戰線同時進行"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T21:37:19.000Z","msg":"但真係要學習前人經驗。其他方面未準備好，就唔好有前冇後一鋪過。"},{"pid":"4cb045a4fc1523d01343af7dbcaca8c119b1fc5c","tid":2037031,"uid":115988,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T21:38:40.000Z","msg":"早在721中聯辦外臨時立法會宣言；<br />\n又或係10.5商場臨時政府宣言；<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">其實香港人係抗爭早期就已經提出左唯一出路</span><br />\n11月區選大勝甚至出現錯覺係制度下抗爭有出路<br />\n<br />\n可惜政府架空立法會 + 中聯辦全面干預 + 假主席立法會奪權 + 國安法繞過本地立法 etc.<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">制度上既絕望逼使香港人走上唯一出路</span><br />\n<br />\n樓主既一番苦功，提供左具體framework作參考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9417e32236cfde84f11f8bad6a17e96302d82183","tid":2037031,"uid":153938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4cb045a4fc1523d01343af7dbcaca8c119b1fc5c","tid":2037031,"uid":115988,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T21:38:40.000Z","msg":"早在721中聯辦外臨時立法會宣言；<br />\n又或係10.5商場臨時政府宣言；<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">其實香港人係抗爭早期就已經提出左唯一出路</span><br />\n11月區選大勝甚至出現錯覺係制度下抗爭有出路<br />\n<br />\n可惜政府架空立法會 + 中聯辦全面干預 + 假主席立法會奪權 + 國安法繞過本地立法 etc.<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">制度上既絕望逼使香港人走上唯一出路</span><br />\n<br />\n樓主既一番苦功，提供左具體framework作參考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T21:43:16.000Z","msg":"而且曼德拉係有搞經濟圈，而且一啲都唔膠。時間太趕之後再慢慢寫，但起碼希望手足知道，唔好覺得一日兩日就endgame，要對得住走咗嘅人，就更加要有策略有計劃。"},{"pid":"edeea14cb77bc7601a4d45ec50b314035ea99316","tid":2037031,"uid":266621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9417e32236cfde84f11f8bad6a17e96302d82183","tid":2037031,"uid":153938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4cb045a4fc1523d01343af7dbcaca8c119b1fc5c","tid":2037031,"uid":115988,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T21:38:40.000Z","msg":"早在721中聯辦外臨時立法會宣言；<br />\n又或係10.5商場臨時政府宣言；<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">其實香港人係抗爭早期就已經提出左唯一出路</span><br />\n11月區選大勝甚至出現錯覺係制度下抗爭有出路<br />\n<br />\n可惜政府架空立法會 + 中聯辦全面干預 + 假主席立法會奪權 + 國安法繞過本地立法 etc.<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">制度上既絕望逼使香港人走上唯一出路</span><br />\n<br />\n樓主既一番苦功，提供左具體framework作參考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T21:43:16.000Z","msg":"而且曼德拉係有搞經濟圈，而且一啲都唔膠。時間太趕之後再慢慢寫，但起碼希望手足知道，唔好覺得一日兩日就endgame，要對得住走咗嘅人，就更加要有策略有計劃。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T21:48:51.000Z","msg":"長路漫漫，留有用之身睇光復一日"},{"pid":"2ccccdf765ba176ba34503c4528919751031edb7","tid":2037031,"uid":350785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T22:22:39.000Z","msg":"講得好，推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42133c5c014daf2543751f4d52424b68808e91e0","tid":2037031,"uid":153938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T22:31:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/ass